      <profileDesc>
         <particDesc>
            <listPerson>
               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">The name of the original donor has been erased throughout the Ms., but can be deciphered on fol. 98ra as Ḫaylä Śǝllase. The name was mostly replaced by a secondary hand with that of Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus, the baptismal name of däğğazmač Subagadis (1770-1831), who is also mentioned as the donor in Additio 1. Other names added later are: Wäldä Lǝʿul (fols. 33ra, 85vb, 114rb, 119ra, 125vb), Täsfa Maryam (fols. 113va, 118va, 127va), Gäbrä Ṣadǝq (fol. 113va), Wäldä Mikaʾel (fols. 114vb, 119rb) and Wäldä Gäbrǝʾel (fol. 125vb).</persName>
                  <!--ACHTUNG! This is actually paragraphic information identifying the donor. 
                                        Person/persName should only contain the person name, not all the paragraph.-->
               </person>
               <person>
                  <persName corresp="PRS00000"/>
                  <!--other-->
               </person>
            </listPerson>
